        <p>Thrifty provides you with various options to to apply for Fixed Deposit-online, mobile, or by visiting the nearest Thrifty outlet.Here are 5 easy steps in which you can apply for Fixed Deposit online.Additionally, you can drop by at your nearest Thrifty branch and ask any representatives to give you.</p>

        <h4>Internet Banking</h4>
        <p>Customers can book Fixed Deposits through any of the channels listed below:</p>
        <h6><b>Step I</b></h6>
        <p>Login to Internet Banking and select the deposit option</p>
        <h6><b>Step II</b></h6>
        <p>Create on Create Fixed Deposit</p>
        <h6><b>Step III</b></h6>
        <p>Fill in the required account and nominee details</p>
        <h6><b>Step IV</b></h6>
        <p>On confirmation, the selected amount will be debited from your savings account and your fixed deposit will be created instantly.</p>
        <h6><b>Step V</b></h6>
        <p>Post creation, the Fixed Deposit advice will be mailed to your registered e-mail id if you are registered for an e-statement.</p>
